    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, then slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>courgette disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>courgette matchsticks</strong>\u00a0with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-7 min or until softened</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the courgette is cooking, add your <strong>pasta</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the pasta for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked pasta</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the pasta is cooking, cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the courgette has softened, drain your<strong>\u00a0king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan\u00a0and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are cooked, add the <strong>drained pasta </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cr\u00e8me fra\u00eeche</strong> with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80ml] </span><strong>starchy pasta water </strong>and stir everything together until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta \u2013 this is your <strong>lemony prawn & courgette pasta</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/lemony-prawn-and-courgette-gluten-free-spaghetti/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemony prawn & courgette pasta </strong>topped with the <strong>chopped chives</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong> and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
